nodes.text: Around 21 BBY, an unidentified Theed warehouse was taken over by Count Dooku, Cad Bane and other bounty hunters including Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi in the disguise of Rako Hardeen.

The bounty hunters killed all the mechanics who were working in the warehouse, and started their plan upon kidnapping Supreme Chancellor Palpatine on the Festival of Light. Embo, Twazzi, Derrown, Bane and Kenobi were handled a holographic disguise matrix so they could bear a particular disguise, while Moralo Eval and Dooku remained in the background, waiting for the outcome of their plan.
